Bibliographic References: PAdd, no. A 113; CVA, pi. 32,1 and 4.
Imagery Description: (a) Standing draped woman with wreath in r. hand, cista and fillet in 1., by stele, (b) standing nude youth with wreath in r. hand, thyrsus and beadNon Sepcifiedwreath in 1.
Additional Notes: The draped woman on this vase is very like the one on no. 448 and on Madrid 11243 (no. 484 below).
